 DAs occurs when\nthey cool below Teff about 105,000 K. We discuss the possibility that the\npaucity of very hot DAs is a consequence of their fast evolutionary rate.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 18 Dec 2018 17:12:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-12-26"}
