reases, the\nproposed ESN approach improves the prediction accuracy. Finally, we demonstrate\nthat throughput gains of about 17% are achieved.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 18 Dec 2018 22:10:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 4 Jun 2019 09:28:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-06-05"}
