de quantum design\nguidelines at the molecular scale to optimize both energy transfer speed and\nrange over macroscopic distances in artificial light-harvesting architectures.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 19 Dec 2018 12:13:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 29 Apr 2019 12:18:17 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 20 Jul 2021 13:40:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-13"}
